parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaDe.Maybe we’re looking in the wrong area. Certainly if the cops can’t find anything, there must not be anything back here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.Don’t be so sure. These guys aren’t detectives.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFlEx.Okay, smart guy. Maybe you can find something.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFlEx.If you’re so smart, then see if you can find what that key goes to.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Bobby sent me here. What did you see?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "OaBaEx.I heard a sound and came to investigate. I saw two people run into the woods as soon as I opened the door.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "OaBaEx.I couldn’t tell. But I’m not going back there to find out. At least not in the dark.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Shit. I better be careful not to get caught.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Shit. I better be careful not to get caught.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NPC.How the hell are we supposed to make progress when all directions are blocked?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NPC.Where did that Guild guy run off to? How did he get past all this brush?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NPC.This is hopeless. Where are we supposed to go?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.The rock here looks weak and crumbly.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.I need something to break this rock loose.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.The wood in this barrel looks very dry. I wonder if it’s meant for burning.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.These weeds are thick and covered in thorns.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.I can see a book up in the tree. I wonder if I could throw something at it and knock it down.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.Diana… I’m risking a lot to help you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiFrOp.I know. I won’t betray your trust.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.Not the easiest thing to believe from a Guild member.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.The Guild might die with or without you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaEx.It opens a locked door in the abandoned chapel.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiFlEx.The secret back entrance to the bunker.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaEx.I’m going to the warehouse to draw the guards to the entrance.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiFlEx.I know how to break in… I just have to get caught.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.And then I sneak in the back and help save your friend, Henry?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.What are you going to do after you get caught?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaEx.There’s a security system in the bunker that will set off if they don’t come to the entrance.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaEx.They have to turn it off in order to surface… If I fail, the trap will trigger.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaEx.Be careful, 1Hero. If you can’t make it to Henry, you need to escape.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.I hope I’m helping the right people.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "OcShOp^.Hey! What are you doing back here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Shit! Duncan’s goons are here. I’m going to get seen.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Shit! Duncan’s goons are here. I’m going to get seen.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Shit! Duncan’s goons are here. I’m going to get seen.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiAnEx.You’re lucky Henry is convinced to help you. I wanted to put a bullet in Duncan’s brain and get the hell out of here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFrEx^.My name is Arianna. I am an angel from the Empyrean.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrBaEx.There’s no time to explain. Follow me.");
